verbose_text: Compared with the transformants expressing pDR196, MtSWEET5b allowed the uptake of fructose, glucose, galactose, and mannose, MtSWEET7 enabled the uptake of glucose, galactose, and mannose but not fructose, while MtSWEET3c was able to restore the growth on the medium supplemented with glucose and mannose (XREF_FIG A).
evidence: MtSWEET5b allowed the uptake of fructose, glucose, galactose
